o Coulomb effects\nand nuclear diffraction. The calculation of the direct and recoil Coulomb\neffects separately and of their interference is the new and most relevant\naspect of this paper.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Nov 2012 18:28:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-12"}
