t the central black hole could be\nconsiderably larger than expected in other formation scenarios for ultracompact\ndwarfs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Nov 2012 21:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 18 Feb 2014 02:07:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-12"}
