 bremsstrahlung do not suffer from\nsuch difficulties.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Nov 2012 21:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 16 May 2013 14:21:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-05-17"}
